window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Already conquered the Multiverse, have you? Well, do it faster!</p> <p>Behold the Multiverse! Its countless realms overflow with terrific opportunities and terrible dangers—warring sects, priceless treasures, martial techniques, and all manner of horrible monsters abound.</p> <p>And Dorian has conquered them all.</p> <p>He’s a Godking—one of the most powerful creatures to ever exist. And as he sits from his throne at the literal summit of the world, bored out of his mind, one question comes to mind: what now?</p> <p>Do it all again, of course! But faster.</p> <p>Don't miss the start of this exciting LitRPG Cultivation Adventure about an ancient God who's reached the peak of his power. So like any true gamer, he decides to start fresh in his conquering of the multiverse and aim for the impossible: A Perfect Run.</p>"; 
